n &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11041,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/quraysh-persecute-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":4310,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Persecution: The Quraysh persecute the Prophet for preaching","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir ibn Abdullah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would present himself to people and he said, \u201cIs there a man who can take me to his people? Verily, the Quraysh have prevented me from preaching the word of my Lord.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2925 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":735,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/04\/27\/ummah-destroyed-young-foolish\/","url_meta":{"origin":4310,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ruin: Muslims led astray by the young, foolish","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe destruction of my nation is at the hands of young men from the Quraysh tribe.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6649 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Bukhari \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0636\u06